file.name: dict_test.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Test openapi spec file for dictionary field
  version: v1
paths:
  /hello:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TestModel'

components:
  schemas:
     
    TestModel:
      description: Model information
      properties:
        stringDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: string
        dateDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: string
            format: date
        intDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: integer
        int32Dict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        int64Dict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: integer
            format: int64
        floatDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: number
            format: float
        doubleDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: number
            format: double
        numberDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: number
        tagDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tag'
        objectDict:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: object
    Tag:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          description: Tag ID
          allOf:
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Id'
        name:
          description: Tag name
          type: string
          minLength: 1
      xml:
        name: Tag
    Id:
      type: integer
      format: int64
      readOnly: true
